io.druid.query

Class QueryToolChest<ResultType,QueryType extends Query<ResultType>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.druid.query.QueryToolChest<ResultType,QueryType>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GroupByQueryQueryToolChest, SearchQueryQueryToolChest, SegmentMetadataQueryQueryToolChest, SelectQueryQueryToolChest, TimeBoundaryQueryQueryToolChest, TimeseriesQueryQueryToolChest, TopNQueryQueryToolChest

    public abstract class QueryToolChest<ResultType,QueryType extends Query<ResultType>>
extends Object
    The broker-side (also used by server in some cases) API for a specific Query type. This API is still undergoing evolution and is only semi-stable, so proprietary Query implementations should be ready for the potential maintenance burden when upgrading versions.
